&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;At Senra Systems, we believe that the future of manufacturing lies not in automation, but in configuration.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We supercharge electrical wire harness manufacturing through software configuration, transforming skilled assembly tasks into high-throughput production lines. We enable customers to design what they want, when they want it and deliver harness builds at record-breaking speed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you will work as an early member of our manufacturing team to build wire harness assemblies and operate machinery. You will also work closely with other engineers and other technicians to design, develop, and iterate on the material process flow for the factory. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll own:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;●&quot; data-font=&quot;&quot; data-listid=&quot;2&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Work in a high pace environment to manufacture wire harnesses for critical aerospace and defense applications&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;●&quot; data-font=&quot;&quot; data-listid=&quot;2&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Responsible for cutting wires, running complex machinery, and labeling applications&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;●&quot; data-font=&quot;&quot; data-listid=&quot;2&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Be involved in ideation, planning, and execution stages of product development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;●&quot; data-font=&quot;&quot; data-listid=&quot;2&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Manufacturing electrical harness assemblies, including ability to correctly interpret schematics and build compliant electrical assemblies as well as demonstrated knowledge of basic electrical tests such as continuity and insulation resistance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;●&quot; data-font=&quot;&quot; data-listid=&quot;2&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Work cross-functionally with teams across the organization to understand their technology needs and build solutions accordingly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;●&quot; data-font=&quot;&quot; data-listid=&quot;2&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Write documentation for development processes and operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;●&quot; data-font=&quot;&quot; data-listid=&quot;2&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Adapt to change quickly and stay up-to-date with new technologies and tools that can benefit the organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;●&quot; data-font=&quot;&quot; data-listid=&quot;2&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Occasionally provide technical support to customers and help improve the overall customer experience, eventually participate in on-call rotation as the company grows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;●&quot; data-font=&quot;&quot; data-listid=&quot;2&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;Support ad-hoc projects to bo

&lt;p&gt;If you are excited to help out but don&#39;t know where to start, consider a general application! We are always on the lookout for candidates who have high aptitude, are excellent team players, and are solution-oriented thinkers that are always excited to challenge the norm.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrate a commitment to our core values, including giving a damn about your work, being transparent, having a growth mindset, being a pleasant person, and having fun.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate effectively with colleagues, support team efforts, and contribute positively to the company culture, ensuring mutual success and growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apply creativity and technical skills to develop and implement solutions that enhance factory operations, streamline processes, and drive technological advancements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a high standard of quality in all tasks, ensuring precision and accuracy whether working on hardware or software projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Embrace new challenges, continuously seek opportunities for learning and development, and be willing to wear multiple hats to support various aspects of the factory operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We are an equal opportunity employer and value diversity at our company. We do not discriminate based on race, religion, color, national origin, gender, sexual orientation, age, marital status, veteran status, or disability status. Contact us at&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:jobs@senrasystems.us&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;jobs@senrasystems.us&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;or visit our website&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://senrasystems.us/&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;https://senrasystems.us&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ITAR REQUIREMENTS:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To conform to U.S. Government export regulations, applicant must be a (i) U.S. citizen or national, (ii) U.S. lawful, permanent resident (aka green card holder), (iii) Refugee under 8 U.S.C. § 1157, or (iv) Asylee under 8 U.S.C. § 1158, or be eligible to obtain the required authorizations from the U.S. Department of State. Learn more about the ITAR&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.pmddtc.state.gov/?id=ddtc_kb_article_page&amp;amp;sys_id=24d528fddbfc930044f9ff621f961987&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;At Senra Systems, we believe that the future of manufacturing lies not in automation, but in configuration.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We supercharge electrical wire harness manufacturing through software configuration, transforming skilled assembly tasks into high-throughput production lines. We enable customers to design what they want, when they want it and deliver harness builds at record-breaking speed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Overview:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are hiring a Recruiter to play a key role in scaling our organization. Over the next year, we expect to significantly grow headcount across both our manufacturing operations and corporate functions as we launch our second factory. This role will be central to supporting that growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will own full cycle hiring across the business — from high volume technician roles to critical corporate positions spanning Engineering, Finance, Sales, and G&amp;amp;A. This role requires range: you&#39;ll need to move quickly on production floor hiring while also running rigorous, relationship-driven searches for office and professional roles.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for someone who can build durable hiring pipelines, move quickly without sacrificing quality, and make hiring decisions that support long term performance and retention.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Will Own:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Recruitment&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operate with a high degree of ownership in a lean recruiting team, setting priorities and driving hiring outcomes with minimal overhead.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive full cycle recruiting for hourly and salaried manufacturing and corporate roles including, but not limited to:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Production and Harness Technicians&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manufacturing Engineers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Quality Technicians and Quality Engineers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Production Leads, Supervisors, and Operations support roles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Software Engineers &amp;amp; Product Managers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute sustained high-volume technician hiring while maintaining hiring quality and retention.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with manufacturing leaders to influence hiring decisions and reset expectations based on market realities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with functional leaders to deeply understand role requirements, team dynamics, and the profiles most likely to succeed at a startup in a scaling phase.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Balance competing priorities across business functions while maintaining responsiveness and quality on all open roles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Pipeline Strategy&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively source candidates through outbound channels including LinkedIn, Indeed, referrals, trade schools, university programs, and local workforce programs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain pipelines for high priority and hard to fill roles across both manufacturing and corporate functions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify post hire performance gaps and adjust sourcing and screening accordingly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adapt hiring plans as business priorities and headcount needs evolve.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Hiring Quality&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct structured screens tailored to each role — assessing technical fit for engineering and finance roles, drive and commercial instincts for sales, reliability and hands-on capability for manufacturing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assess coachability, learning ability, direct communication, low ego and high ownership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;At Senra Systems, we believe that the future of manufacturing lies not in automation, but in configuration.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We supercharge electrical wire harness manufacturing through software configuration, transforming skilled assembly tasks into high-throughput production lines. We enable customers to design what they want, when they want it and deliver harness builds at record-breaking speed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Harnessing Technician, you will be a key member of our production team, building critical aerospace and defense electrical harness assemblies with minimal supervision. You will work closely with engineers, specialists, and other technicians to deliver high-quality builds while contributing to the continuous improvement of our factory systems. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll own:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manufacture intermediate to complex wire harnesses independently following schematics and work instructions. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interpret technical schematics and drawings to ensure accurate assembly. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform soldering, crimping, routing, and strain relief using best practices and quality standards.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Troubleshoot basic build issues and escalate blockers to supervisors or engineering teams. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the documentation of processes and suggest improvements where needed. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentor Apprentice Technicians and support team training initiatives. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in daily floor meetings, audits, and continuous improvement activities. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support ad-hoc projects to boost output and ensure harness builds are delivered quickly and efficiently.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll bring to the team:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;High school diploma or equivalent certification.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;1–7 years of experience in electrical harness manufacturing or related technical fields.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:6}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Proficient in interpreting intermediate to complex schematics.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:6}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Ability to perform soldering, crimping, and basic troubleshooting.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:6}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Ability to lift up to 25 lbs. unassisted and stand for extended periods.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:6}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;At Senra Systems, we believe that the future of manufacturing lies not in automation, but in configuration.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We supercharge electrical wire harness manufacturing through software configuration, transforming skilled assembly tasks into high-throughput production lines. We enable customers to design what they want, when they want it and deliver harness builds at record-breaking speed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We are looking for a Head of Customer Programs to lead the organization responsible for customer engagement, technical program management, estimating, quoting, and long-term account growth.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;This is a highly visible executive leadership role with direct interaction with the COO, CEO, and CTPO.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;The&amp;nbsp;Head&amp;nbsp;of Customer Programs &amp;amp; Estimating&amp;nbsp;is responsible for&amp;nbsp;building and leading the customer-facing engine that converts customer demand into profitable, repeat production business.&amp;nbsp;This leader will oversee all estimating, quoting, program management, technical program management, customer communications, and account growth activities. They will be accountable for customer experience, quote conversion, estimating accuracy, organizational scalability, and long-term revenue growth.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;This role requires a unique blend of manufacturing&amp;nbsp;expertise, commercial acumen, technical credibility, leadership capability, and operational discipline.&amp;nbsp;The ideal candidate has spent&amp;nbsp;significant time&amp;nbsp;in high-growth manufacturing environments and understands both how products are built and how customers are won and&amp;nbsp;retained.&amp;nbsp;This role will require up to 25% of travel time as&amp;nbsp;required.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;Organization&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;TextRun SCXW17492866 BCX0&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;NormalTextRun SCXW17492866 BCX0&quot;&gt;The&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;NormalTextRun SCXW17492866 BCX0&quot;&gt;Head&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;NormalTextRun SCXW17492866 BCX0&quot;&gt;of Customer Programs &amp;amp; Estimating will lead the teams responsible for customer

